OL,3,CPlans to merge police forces would be
OL,4,C'disaster', says top official
OL,6,FSurrey's Police and Crime Commissioner
OL,7,F(PCC) has decried the Government's
OL,8,Fplans to merge police forces in the
OL,9,FSouth into a single unit.
OL,11,FLisa Townsend, Surrey PCC, said the
OL,12,Fmove to combine forces in Surrey,
OL,13,FSussex, the Thames Valley, Kent, and
OL,14,FHampshire would not benefit local
OL,15,Fresidents.
OL,17,FTownsend claimed the merger would see
OL,18,Fresources diverted away from local
OL,19,Fcommunities. "I make no bones about
OL,20,Fit, I believe Surrey residents deserve
OL,21,Fbetter than this," she said.
OL,26,@{D@NOU
