PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781777898
OL,3,CPlans to merge police forces would be
OL,4,C'disaster', says top official
OL,6,F"We are the safest county in the south
OL,7,Feast with no city and much lower crime
OL,8,Frates than our neighbours."
OL,10,FShe added: "I am concerned that a
OL,11,Fmerger with other forces would result
OL,12,Fin resources being pulled away from
OL,13,Four communities to support higher
OL,14,Fcrime areas leaving Surrey with a
OL,15,Fsecond-rate service."
OL,26,@rD@LOU
