OL,3,CPlans to merge police forces would be
OL,4,C'disaster', says top official
OL,6,FThe reforms were announced by the
OL,7,FGovernment in January, as part of a
OL,8,Freview into policing across England
OL,9,Fand Wales. It described the plans as a
OL,10,F"move towards a more efficient
OL,11,Fpolicing system (...) built around
OL,12,Ffewer, larger police forces."
OL,14,FA Government White Paper outlining
OL,15,Fdetails of the changes, said there are
OL,16,Fcurrently 43 separate police force in
OL,17,FEngland Wales based on a structure
OL,18,Fwhich was set out in the 1960s and 70s.
OL,26,@sD@QpmsD@Upn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
