PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781777898
OL,3,CPlans to merge police forces would be
OL,4,C'disaster', says top official
OL,6,FIt said reducing the number of forces
OL,7,Fcould bring down costs and provide a
OL,8,Fmore consistent service for members of
OL,9,Fthe public across different regions.
OL,11,FTownsend, however, has refuted those
OL,12,Fclaims and opened a survey for locals
OL,13,Fresidents to have their say on the
OL,14,Fpotential changes.
OL,16,F"This is really important for the
OL,17,Ffuture of policing and although the
OL,18,FGovernment are drawing the plans up,
OL,19,Fthe public are not being consulted,"
OL,20,Fshe explained.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
