CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781777898
OL,3,CPlans to merge police forces would be
OL,4,C'disaster', says top official
OL,6,F"I want to ensure the public of Surrey
OL,7,Fhave a voice and that is why I am
OL,8,Fasking everyone to take a few minutes
OL,9,Fto fill out my survey and have their
OL,10,Fsay.
OL,12,F"I will publish the results later this
OL,13,Fsummer and share them with those who
OL,14,Fare making the decisions around force
OL,15,Fmergers."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
