PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781777898
OL,3,CPlans to merge police forces would be
OL,4,C'disaster', says top official
OL,6,FShe added: "Police reform is
OL,7,Fabsolutely necessary and of course we
OL,8,Fmust continue to modernise. We face
OL,9,Fincreasingly difficult threats from
OL,10,Fcyber and organised crime and we want
OL,11,Fto work with the Government to create
OL,12,Fbetter ways to tackle issues
OL,13,Fnationally.
OL,26,@nD@LOU
