PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781777898
OL,3,CPlans to merge police forces would be
OL,4,C'disaster', says top official
OL,6,F"In my opinion, the creation of
OL,7,Fregional forces would not only be
OL,8,Fexpensive and complex to deliver, but
OL,9,Fhere in Surrey would result in the
OL,10,Fdilution of both the service our
OL,11,Fresidents rightly expect and local
OL,12,Faccountability ` particularly in light
OL,13,Fof the abolition of directly elected
OL,14,FPCCs.
OL,16,F"I'm a firm believer that local
OL,17,Fpolicing needs to be left to local
OL,18,Fpolice forces to deliver.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
