PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1781777898
OL,3,CPlans to merge police forces would be
OL,4,C'disaster', says top official
OL,6,F"At a time when we need to rebuild
OL,7,Fpublic confidence in policing, my view
OL,8,Fis these merger plans will only
OL,9,Fdistance our policing teams from the
OL,10,Fcommunities they serve."
OL,26,@rD@XO]
